ygData.messageBody:
I am interested in getting this Man O'war , and i heard it has to do from a
quest from the Dwarven Paladin guild, so i went there and i hailed each and
every one of them, but my faction is too sucky to get a decent response from
them other than, "Half elves like you are a disgrace to Norrath" .. and
other things like that

so my question is, anybody know a way to get faction with these buggers, i
cant do one of their quests, because i cant get a quest out of them, any
monsters i can kill? or quests from any other kaladim guilds that will give
me some faction to Clerics of Underfoot?

any info qould be appreciated, thx!

-Schank Shagwell
-25th Paladin of E'ci
